entry.title: Duterte aides to be ‘bridges’ between MECQ areas, gov’t agencies: Nograles

media:group.media:title: Duterte aides to be ‘bridges’ between MECQ areas, gov’t agencies: Nograles
media:group.media:description: President Rodrigo Duterte’s aides will act as “bridges” between national government agencies and local officials in Metro Manila and other areas under the second strictest lockdown level to contain the coronavirus pandemic, Cabinet Secretary Karlo Nograles said Friday.

entry.title: Gov’t to study engineers’ recommendation on motorcycle shields

media:group.media:title: Gov’t to study engineers’ recommendation on motorcycle shields
media:group.media:description: An inter-agency task force (IATF) will study engineers’ recommendations on its policy for installing protective dividers for pillion riding on motorcycles to prevent the spread of the novel coronavirus, Cabinet Secretary Karlo Nograles said Friday.

entry.title: Ospital ng Tondo closed for 10 days after 32 doctors, nurses fall ill

media:group.media:title: Ospital ng Tondo closed for 10 days after 32 doctors, nurses fall ill
media:group.media:description: MANILA - The Ospital ng Tondo in Manila will stop accepting patients for 10 days after 32 doctors and nurses fell ill after tending to COVID-19 patients, Mayor Isko Moreno said Friday.
